text: John Brunton (23 July 1869 - 12 November 1962) was an English cricketer. He played six first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club in 1894. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1869 births Category:1962 deaths Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:Cricketers from Varanasi
